result.name: pendle-procurement-contract-register
result.notes:
This dataset details a list of the contracts currently in place at Pendle Council.

As part of the Local Government Transparency Code 2014, we are required to publish our existing household waste collection contract where there is one in place.  However, as this is a service delivered in-house (i.e. by Pendle Council) this is not applicable.
result.title: Pendle Procurement - Contract Register
